{"id":124128,"type":6,"name":"邊城浪子","image":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/m/29/2b/124128_BvaDf.jpg","summary":"二十年前，一宗梅花庵外的灭门血案，轰动武林，二十年后，该血案主角的遗孤傅红雪长大，实行万里追凶，在沈三娘的暗助下，查出自己原来并非真正受害人的后代，但他的情人翠浓已为他牺牲了。另一方面，小李飞刀的传人叶关一心追寻身世，始知自己与此血案有莫大关连，令致一直追随他的丁灵琳带疚离去。最后，凶手之理马空郡不但天网恢恢，还连累了女儿的一生。目睹此一切，身世如谜的儿子决与傅红雪大战一场，以作了断......","info":"<li><span>中文名: </span>边城浪子</li><li><span>原作: </span><a href=\"/person/16836\">古龍</a></li><li><span>监制: </span><a href=\"/person/16552\">王天林</a></li><li><span>主演: </span><a href=\"/person/16623\">張兆輝</a>、<a href=\"/person/16706\">曾華倩</a>、<a href=\"/person/16939\">吳岱融</a>、谢宁、梁艺龄、<a href=\"/person/16929\">高妙思</a>、欧瑞伟、<a href=\"/person/16951\">謝寧</a>、<a href=\"/person/17919\">歐瑞偉</a>、<a href=\"/person/16557\">梁藝齡</a></li><li><span>配角: </span><a href=\"/person/16441\">駱應鈞</a></li><li><span>集数: </span>20</li><li><span>开始: </span>1989</li><li><span>类型: </span>武侠</li><li><span>国家/地区: </span>香港</li><li><span>每集长: </span>43分钟</li><li><span>电视台: </span>TVB</li>","eps":[{"id":476456,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476456","type":0,"sort":1,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476457,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476457","type":0,"sort":2,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476458,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476458","type":0,"sort":3,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476459,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476459","type":0,"sort":4,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476460,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476460","type":0,"sort":5,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476461,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476461","type":0,"sort":6,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":"","comment":0,"desc":"","status":"Air"},{"id":476462,"url":"http://bgm.tv/ep/476462","type":0,"sort":7,"name":"","name_cn":"","duration":"","airdate":""